{"tid":1427594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解有人覺得唔洗再打輿論戰？","createTime":"2019-08-07T06:53:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T07:38:19.000Z","uid":105358,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f2e56a27de56577f45f3d8bad5e9be1eba091da2","tid":1427594,"uid":105358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:53:17.000Z","msg":"點解有人覺得大眾會光速接受抗爭，民意唔洗爭？<br />\n林奠、紅媒、中共已經全力抹黑義士，抽離場運動既因果<br />\n指我地想「反中亂港」<br />\n<br />\n一、<span style=\"color: blue;\">抹黑我地唔係為香港企出嚟</span>，揾藉口搞亂香港，推翻一國<br />\n<code>以修例工作為借口所產生既局面　&mdash;林鄭 8.4</code><br />\n<code>止暴制亂 &mdash;張曉明 8.7</code><br />\n<br />\n二、繼續分化，勇武派<span style=\"color: blue;\">前線野蠻有企圖</span>，後排和理非係被誤導肯溝通<br />\n<code>日前曾與示威者傾談，站在最前線人士的回應不友善；亦有不少人說，若政府撤回修例，成立獨立委員會，至少一半人不再出來示威　&mdash;田北晨 8.7</code><br />\n<br />\n三、重上道德高地，以本土角度言說<br />\n<code>我地呢面全體都係以香港為家既人，我地冇第二個家，要維護香港既發展　&mdash;譚惠珠 8.7</code><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">_____________________________________________________</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n輿論戰方向，我結論好簡單，行動文宣同民間記者會重申舊調<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一，光復香港 時代革命</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&mdash;唔係叫革命就港獨，文化大革命都冇推翻中共啦</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">二，掉核彈都唔割蓆</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&mdash;但做錯一定會批評</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">三，前線係深愛香港既人</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&mdash;正正佢地想下一代安定先行出嚟</span><br />\n</span></strong>"},{"pid":"f0ba26f14b4ae0e9d4ca2f790154bbbfa8a2e936","tid":1427594,"uid":60049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:54:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e8163466c3862e3a0a3652013a54f1728f7a5fd","tid":1427594,"uid":157891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:06:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7fcb2506b4d67685e074946a7d5333fc90eb699d","tid":1427594,"uid":232817,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:07:06.000Z","msg":"根本一路要做，係開始有班人，我唔敢亂話佢地五毛，係度吹話唔洗再理民意，根本ON9"},{"pid":"1d3ebf22e12d37756a8831d2d61bda7446a5ec24","tid":1427594,"uid":157891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:12:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"723d025efecbbaa90c853be77fed901d5f72ff12","tid":1427594,"uid":273747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:13:15.000Z","msg":"推..話唔洗理民意既都ON撚9<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3121d52380a1e87c220f809c30ebdc1743bb7356","tid":1427594,"uid":50457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:13:42.000Z","msg":"輿論一定要打"},{"pid":"3f1f8ee2141874b62791f056986d3cb07b63874f","tid":1427594,"uid":49462,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:13:42.000Z","msg":"推 輿論戰比想像中重要好多"},{"pid":"ad61e70ae880054bd21187b93235fce03206a027","tid":1427594,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:13:59.000Z","msg":"贏咪民意囉<br />\n根本我地做左咁多野 民意都無變過<br />\n法國同烏克蘭既群眾示威 佢地有無理過民意？"},{"pid":"97336cbcdae42dc37a00c6a134fc80dcb8398c05","tid":1427594,"uid":49462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"723d025efecbbaa90c853be77fed901d5f72ff12","tid":1427594,"uid":273747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:13:15.000Z","msg":"推..話唔洗理民意既都ON撚9<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:14:47.000Z","msg":"真 做乜都要有人支持先可以持續落去"},{"pid":"b710e10f3fd532eac4f1356a94f3e659b35619b4","tid":1427594,"uid":49462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad61e70ae880054bd211